    <p>The at­trac­tion, home to 900 an­i­mals rep­re­sent­ing more than 100 species, has re­opened with safe man­age­ment mea­sures in place. For in­stance, vis­i­tor ca­pac­ity has been cut to</p>
    <p>25 per cent and seats are limited to 50 at the an­i­mal shows. There is a pro­mo­tion for lo­cal res­i­dents till</p>
